{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cc6ca26e59","title":"中共中央通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4980eaa509","index":0,"year":1971,"month":10,"day":3,"articleId":"cc6ca26e59"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3c11982f62","name":"汪东兴","type":"人物"},{"id":"471a503675","name":"张春桥","type":"人物"},{"id":"9a50528209","name":"纪登奎","type":"人物"},{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"f3ee2f4a99","name":"李德生","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","name":"中共党史教学参考资料 第26册 “文化大革命”参考资料 中册（1988年）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b.pdf"}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"45707997cd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席批示：同意","index":0,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"d43b5ed272","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央通知","index":1,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"8875a31262","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九七一年九月二十九日）","index":2,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"41f6f59f78","type":"paragraph","text":"中央鉴于黄永胜、吴法宪、李作鹏、邱会作四同志参加林、陈反党集团的宗派活动，陷人很深、实难继续现任工作，已令他们高职反省，彻底交代","index":3,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"e26668318e","type":"paragraph","text":"军委日常工作，中央已决定由军委副主席叶剑英同志主持，并筹组军委办公会议，进行集体领导。毛主席批示：同意","index":4,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"f09f49a24e","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央通知","index":5,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"f13e2f8ebb","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九七一年十月三日","index":6,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"9b033b9e0b","type":"paragraph","text":"为彻底审查、弄清林——陈反党集团的问题，中央决定成立中央专案组，集中处理有关问题，中央专案组由周恩来、康生、江青、张春桥、姚文元、纪登奎、李德生、汪东兴、吴德、吴忠十人组成。在专案组领导下，设立工作机构，由纪登奎、汪东兴两同志负责进行日常工作。各地、各单位今后凡向中央上报有关林-—陈反党集团的揭发材料，统请以绝密亲启件送交中央专案组统一处理。毛主席批示：同意","index":7,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"7d33ea8277","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央通知","index":8,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"fe1cc7a69c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九七一年十一月三日）","index":9,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"},{"id":"cb25068b30","type":"paragraph","text":"中央决定，撤消军委办事组，成立军委办公会议。军委办公会议由军委副主席叶剑英同志主持，并由叶剑英、谢富治、张春桥、李先念、李德生、纪登奎、汪东兴、陈士集、张才千、刘贤权十同志组成，即日成立，在中央军委领导下负责军委日常工作，特此通知","index":10,"publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59"}],"page":{"id":"dee596e350","publicationId":"34799034-2c67-4e1f-ae74-793ab6bd754b","articleId":"cc6ca26e59","start":655,"end":655}}}},"__N_SSG":true}